<item>
            <title>[LU-3687] several sanity tests are failed if run separately because of parent directory d0.sanity does not exist</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3687</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;test_mkdir() creates parent directory only if called with -p option.&lt;br/&gt;
Several sanity tests are failed to create $tdir if run separately because of parent directory d0.sanity does not exist and test_mkdir () is called without -p option&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;# ONLY=6g sh sanity.sh
== sanity test 6g: Is &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; dir in sgid dir inheriting group? == 03:34:51 (1374046491)
 sanity test_6g: @@@@@@ FAIL: mkdir f.sanity.6g failed 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
